{"tid":1823730,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"特首稱單程證是為家庭團聚　改動政策不是考慮方案","createTime":"2020-01-14T02:35:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-14T04:04:19.000Z","uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"c385a6709f0b28173031180df8bba5b22b64c4e0","tid":1823730,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T02:35:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n廣東省政協常委、新地執行董事郭基煇在廣東省政協十二屆三次會議上，提出把單程證上限由每日150個削減至75個。行政長官林鄭月娥被問到是否有可能做到這個建議，以及這個建議是否能達到紓緩中港兩地之間的誤解。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥說，單程證政策是為了家庭團聚，必須尊重讓家庭可以一同生活，這是人權和自由。她說，在這個時候改動政策或名額會帶出訊息，會將某一社會現象，推向家庭團聚的政策，這個不是政府考慮中的方案。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥說，現時單程證名額仍是150個是按政策和需要，由內地機關審批，而過去兩年沒有用盡，因為不想造成現象，有太多人利用這個制度來港定居。現時配偶分隔兩地的個案仍要輪候4年，現時有3分1屬跨境婚姻。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1502661-20200114.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1502661-20200114.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=x7%2Fg1uS4a%2BT3911x%2BwLoHAOzzNjRw9ZJ5YgnvwIkb18%3D&h=75f30eda\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1502661-20200114.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=0e3e1141\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1502661-20200114.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"72b76308ec00a045a33d5f1e2cba2ee9d5e2496e","tid":1823730,"uid":14494,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T02:36:26.000Z","msg":"笑死人 4大家族以為捐左幾塊地就有話語權<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />依家中共係要晒你副身家呀傻鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"434dffe2f59e26b718bd2a870c1a28b6c4b8ef3a","tid":1823730,"uid":343643,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T02:36:53.000Z","msg":"柒婆學人講人權和自由<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\